    </a>
   </div>
   <dl class="meta">
    <dt>Date</dt>
    <dd>Tue, 10 Dec 1996 22:49:21 -0800</dd>
    <dt>From</dt>
    <dd>Mike West &lt;mwest@CDSNET.NET&gt;</dd>
